{{package|sys-apps/portage}} is Gentoo's [[package manager]], and is installed by default as part of the stage3 install. See the [http://www.gentoo.org/doc/en/handbook/ Gentoo Handbook] for more details.

== Overlays ==
In addition to the official repository (colloquially known as "portage" because of its traditional placement in {{path|/usr/portage/}}), there are additional repositories which in Gentoo are called ''[[overlay]]s''.

* [http://www.gentoo.org/proj/en/overlays/userguide.xml Gentoo Overlays: Users' Guide]
* [http://layman.sourceforge.net/ Layman homepage]
* [http://gpo.zugaina.org/ Browse overlays]

You can search through the ebuilds available in the overlays on http://overlays.gentoo.org/ by using [[eix]].

